The Hello Wall

An installation by Hellicar&Lewis.
http://thehellowall.com
http://hellicarandlewis.com

Compatible with of_preRelease_v0061_osxSL_FAT

http://openframeworks.cc
http://openframeworks.cc/download

Thanks to the whole OpenFrameworks community.

Uses TWURL for interfacing with Twitter:

https://github.com/marcel/twurl

You will need to install TWURL on your machine in order to use this sofware.

Draws upon development of Twitter addons by members of the OpenFrameworks community.

Principally:

Todd Vanderlin
http://toddvanderlin.com

and

simongeilfus
http://www.openframeworks.cc/forum/viewtopic.php?f=10&t=2750

Also uses:

ofxBox2D by Todd Vanderlin
http://toddvanderlin.com

ofxTweener by Erik Sjodin

